      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAPID LULU (1) was a winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 10 length third at Q Parklands (30.81). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Sure to be about the mark. EASTLY BREEZE (3) stalked the lead from the inside draw before finishing second last start (22.23) at this track in Mix 5 over 390m. Hard to beat again. TASTE LIKE HONEY (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Q Straight following on from a second place finish (19.63) there the start prior. Likely to play a prominent role. MAJESTIC ZEAL (8) drops in distance and is not to be underestimated.",
